Class Job

java.lang.Object
  Job

public class Job
extends java.lang.Object

Job Class is a data keeping class intended to be used as an object to be passed to and from the it contains private variables ArrivalTime - the time the job arrived in the system LLQ - the last queue it was placed on PID - the ID Number of the Job and queueArrival - the time at which the job arrived in a queue

Version:
Final, 04/06/2017
Author:
Eric Davey
